Thompson-Herah helps to associate the brand with speed, said Geoff Lowery, analyst at Redburn in London.\", \"from\": 487, \"to\": 766, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 567, \"end\": 574, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9999896976217778, \"rank\": 1.0300069370627328e-05, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}, {\"begin\": 634, \"end\": 650, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shericka_Jackson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shericka Jackson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shericka_Jackson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shericka_Jackson\"}, {\"begin\": 655, \"end\": 676, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elaine_Thompson-Herah\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Elaine Thompson-Herah\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elaine_Thompson-Herah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elaine_Thompson-Herah\"}, {\"begin\": 748, \"end\": 755, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Redburn\", \"score\": 0.9999999998035491, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Redburn\", \"types\": [\"Q571\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Redburn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Redburn\"}, {\"begin\": 759, \"end\": 765, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999591372072606, \"rank\": 4.083439676803273e-05, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Puma\", \"from\": 490, \"to\": 494}, {\"ngram\": \"more everyday and serious runners\", \"from\": 513, \"to\": 546}, {\"ngram\": \"its sponsorship\", \"from\": 548, \"to\": 563}, {\"ngram\": \"the world's best sprinters\", \"from\": 602, \"to\": 628}, {\"ngram\": \"the brand\", \"from\": 696, \"to\": 705}, {\"ngram\": \"speed\", \"from\": 711, \"to\": 716}, {\"ngram\": \"Geoff Lowery\", \"from\": 723, \"to\": 735}, {\"ngram\": \"analyst\", \"from\": 737, \"to\": 744}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You are never going to sell very many running spikes, but in terms of properly iconic teams that credentialise you as a performance brand and associate you with some of the most exciting athletes, Puma have a super-strong relationship there,\\\" Lowery said.\", \"from\": 768, \"to\": 1024, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 966, \"end\": 970, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cougar\", \"score\": 0.9998187724209414, \"rank\": 0.00018125666727872238, \"text\": \"Puma\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cougar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cougar\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"very many running spikes\", \"from\": 797, \"to\": 821}, {\"ngram\": \"terms\", \"from\": 830, \"to\": 835}, {\"ngram\": \"properly iconic teams\", \"from\": 839, \"to\": 860}, {\"ngram\": \"a performance brand\", \"from\": 887, \"to\": 906}, {\"ngram\": \"the most exciting athletes\", \"from\": 938, \"to\": 964}, {\"ngram\": \"a super-strong relationship\", \"from\": 976, \"to\": 1003}, {\"ngram\": \"Lowery\", \"from\": 1012, \"to\": 1018}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Freundt visited Jamaica at the end of March, attending the country's top high school track and field meet for the first time to launch the Jamaican Olympic kit at the event seen as a testing ground for young athletic talent.\", \"from\": 1026, \"to\": 1250, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1042, \"end\": 1049, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9999896976217778, \"rank\": 1.0300069370627328e-05, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}, {\"begin\": 1165, \"end\": 1173, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"score\": 0.9999998394394098, \"rank\": 1.6055550092146084e-07, \"text\": \"Jamaican\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Freundt\", \"from\": 1026, \"to\": 1033}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 1053, \"to\": 1060}, {\"ngram\": \"March\", \"from\": 1064, \"to\": 1069}, {\"ngram\": \"the country's top high school track\", \"from\": 1081, \"to\": 1116}, {\"ngram\": \"field\", \"from\": 1121, \"to\": 1126}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 1136, \"to\": 1150}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 1189, \"to\": 1198}, {\"ngram\": \"a testing ground\", \"from\": 1207, \"to\": 1223}, {\"ngram\": \"young athletic talent\", \"from\": 1228, \"to\": 1249}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We need to be very clear that Puma is about speed,\\\" Freundt, who has been in the top job just over a year, told Reuters in an interview ahead of the campaign launch.\", \"from\": 1252, \"to\": 1418, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1283, \"end\": 1287, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cougar\", \"score\": 0.9998187724209414, \"rank\": 0.00018125666727872238, \"text\": \"Puma\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cougar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cougar\"}, {\"begin\": 1365, \"end\": 1372, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"score\": 0.9999905584975355, \"rank\": 9.39161335071486e-06, \"text\": \"Reuters\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"speed\", \"from\": 1297, \"to\": 1302}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\" Freundt\", \"from\": 1303, \"to\": 1312}, {\"ngram\": \"the top job\", \"from\": 1330, \"to\": 1341}, {\"ngram\": \"an interview\", \"from\": 1376, \"to\": 1388}, {\"ngram\": \"the campaign launch\", \"from\": 1398, \"to\": 1417}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That's something we need to strengthen further in the consumer mindset.\\\"\", \"from\": 1419, \"to\": 1492, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1427, \"to\": 1436}, {\"ngram\": \"the consumer mindset\", \"from\": 1470, \"to\": 1490}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Like other sportswear retailers that sponsor Olympians and pour marketing money into the Games, the bet is that athletes breaking records in Puma gear will nudge spectators towards its whole range of products, creating a potential \\\"halo effect\\\" for everything from marathon shoes to everyday sneakers.\", \"from\": 1494, \"to\": 1795, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"other sportswear retailers\", \"from\": 1499, \"to\": 1525}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympians\", \"from\": 1539, \"to\": 1548}, {\"ngram\": \"marketing money\", \"from\": 1558, \"to\": 1573}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1579, \"to\": 1588}, {\"ngram\": \"the bet\", \"from\": 1590, \"to\": 1597}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 1606, \"to\": 1614}, {\"ngram\": \"breaking records\", \"from\": 1615, \"to\": 1631}, {\"ngram\": \"Puma gear\", \"from\": 1635, \"to\": 1644}, {\"ngram\": \"spectators\", \"from\": 1656, \"to\": 1666}, {\"ngram\": \"its whole range\", \"from\": 1675, \"to\": 1690}, {\"ngram\": \"products\", \"from\": 1694, \"to\": 1702}, {\"ngram\": \"a potential \\\"halo effect\", \"from\": 1713, \"to\": 1737}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1743, \"to\": 1753}, {\"ngram\": \"marathon shoes\", \"from\": 1759, \"to\": 1773}, {\"ngram\": \"everyday sneakers\", \"from\": 1777, \"to\": 1794}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Brands like Puma, Adidas, and Nike will also be allowed to celebrate their Olympic athletes' medal wins on social media during the Games for the first time, as the International Olympic Committee (IOC) plans to relax rules governing online marketing in a \\\"pilot project\\\" with the World Federation of the Sporting Goods Industry.\", \"from\": 1797, \"to\": 2125, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1809, \"end\": 1813, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cougar\", \"score\": 0.9998187724209414, \"rank\": 0.00018125666727872238, \"text\": \"Puma\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cougar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cougar\"}, {\"begin\": 1827, \"end\": 1831, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"score\": 0.9227848005434919, \"rank\": 0.08367623719823265, \"text\": \"Nike\", \"types\": [\"Q728\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\"}, {\"begin\": 1961, \"end\": 1998, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee (IOC)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Brands\", \"from\": 1797, \"to\": 1803}, {\"ngram\": \"Adidas\", \"from\": 1815, \"to\": 1821}, {\"ngram\": \"their Olympic athletes' medal wins\", \"from\": 1866, \"to\": 1900}, {\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 1904, \"to\": 1916}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1924, \"to\": 1933}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 1938, \"to\": 1952}, {\"ngram\": \"rules\", \"from\": 2014, \"to\": 2019}, {\"ngram\": \"online marketing\", \"from\": 2030, \"to\": 2046}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"pilot project\", \"from\": 2050, \"to\": 2066}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Federation\", \"from\": 2073, \"to\": 2093}, {\"ngram\": \"the Sporting Goods Industry\", \"from\": 2097, \"to\": 2124}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"With the new IOC regulations we will be able to use that moment in a better way, to congratulate them [athletes] also via social media, I think that's a win-win for both the Olympics a